.cloner(1) -- clone git repos for worktree workflows

NAME
       cloner - a facilitator for the git worktree workflow

SYNOPSIS
       cloner [options]

DESCRIPTION
       cloner - a wrapper around git clone to setup the directory for the worktree workflow

USAGE

       cloner repo_to_clone

       e.g.

       cloner git@github.com:joshuacox/cloner.git


AUTHOR
       joshua Edward McLauglin Cox
       http://joshuacox.github.io/cloner
